title: Phoebe G and Sophia K Launch Digital Fashion Startup
content: Phoebe Gates, daughter of Bill Gates, and her friend Sophia Kianni are set to launch Phia, an online fashion platform aimed at revolutionizing secondhand shopping.

title: PLD Space Plans 32 Rocket Launches by 2030
content: Spanish startup PLD Space, specializing in the development of Miura rockets, plans to balance its accounts by 2026 and achieve 32 annual launches by 2030.
